.TH cdf-schema 1  "cdf-schema "
.SH NAME
cdf\-schema \- Discover, pin, compare, and promote schemas
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcdf schema\fR [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]... [\fB\-\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-unicode\fR] [\fB\-\-memory\-budget\fR] [\fB\-\-spill\-budget\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Discover, pin, compare, and promote schemas
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress progress and non\-primary success narration
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Show evidence detail; repeat for diagnostics
.TP
\fB\-\-color\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Color policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-progress\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Progress policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-unicode\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Unicode policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-memory\-budget\fR \fI<BYTES>\fR
Process memory budget, e.g. 4GiB or 512MiB
.TP
\fB\-\-spill\-budget\fR \fI<BYTES>\fR
Spill/disk budget, e.g. 64GiB or 512MiB
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
cdf\-schema\-discover(1)
Discover the current physical source schema
.TP
cdf\-schema\-pin(1)
Pin a discovered schema into the project contract
.TP
cdf\-schema\-show(1)
Show the selected durable record
.TP
cdf\-schema\-diff(1)
Compare durable schemas
.TP
cdf\-schema\-promote(1)
Plan or execute residual schema promotion
